# Internal config & definitions — the only private layer.
# Anything under an _internal/ dir at any depth is author-only:
# disguise dictionaries, style guides, lesson-template specs, etc.
# Convention-driven (structural) rather than per-file enumeration so
# new internal content is auto-private without a .gitignore update.
**/_internal/
